---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Connect">
  <section class="py-20 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1.1fr_1fr] gap-16">
    <div>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl text-text-main mb-8 leading-tight">Tell me what's <em class="text-accent italic">actually</em> going on.</h1>
      <p class="font-serif text-2xl text-text-muted italic mb-10 border-l-2 border-primary pl-6">The best conversations I have start with someone saying what they haven't said out loud yet.</p>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-12">
        <p>Maybe your company is sprinting toward AI and something feels off. Maybe you're the only person in the room who thinks the governance question matters. Maybe you read something here that made you think "finally, someone is saying it" — or "this person is wrong about everything."</p>
        <p>All of those are good reasons to get in touch. I read everything, I respond to everything, and I don't run your message through a sales funnel.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-base-light pt-8">
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6">Find me directly</div>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-1">Email</div>
          <a href="mailto:asaf@getclarity.studio" class="font-serif text-2xl text-text-main hover:text-primary transition border-b border-transparent hover:border-primary">asaf@getclarity.studio</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-1">LinkedIn</div>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/asafpel/" target="_blank" class="font-serif text-2xl text-text-main hover:text-primary transition border-b border-transparent hover:border-primary">linkedin.com/in/asafpel</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-base-light p-10 rounded-2xl border border-base-light/50 shadow-2xl h-fit">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl text-text-main mb-4">Or use the form.</h3>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-8 text-sm">Same inbox, less typing into "To:" fields. I'll get back to you within a couple of days.</p>
      
      <form class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <label class="block font-mono text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-2">Your name</label>
          <input type="text" class="w-full bg-base border border-base-light rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-main focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block font-mono text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-2">Email</label>
          <input type="email" class="w-full bg-base border border-base-light rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-main focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block font-mono text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-2">What brings you here?</label>
          <select class="w-full bg-base border border-base-light rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-main focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition appearance-none">
            <option>Pick whatever fits</option>
            <option>We have an AI governance problem</option>
            <option>EU AI Act — we need help</option>
            <option>Just want to connect</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block font-mono text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-2">What's on your mind?</label>
          <textarea rows="4" class="w-full bg-base border border-base-light rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-main focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition placeholder-text-muted/50" placeholder="As much or as little as you want."></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="w-full bg-primary text-black font-semibold py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-accent transition shadow-lg shadow-primary/20">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>